author: markt
msg: The AECDH alias is for "anonymous Elliptic Curve Diffie Hellman cipher suites". Parser was returning non-anonymous ECDH cipher suites.

author: markt
msg: The ECDH alias is for "cipher suites using ECDH key exchange, including anonymous, ephemeral and fixed ECDH". Ephemeral was missing.

author: julianfoad
msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: add Ev3 shims at the RA layer.
(apply_propedit): Pass in the copy-from path and rev so we can look up the
correct base when the node is a copy child. Adjust callers.
(ev3_add_directory): Correct the base revision to SVN_INVALID_REVNUM.
(ev3_add_file): Correct the base rev to SVN_INVALID_REVNUM. Set copyfrom_*.
Also add debug prints (commented out) and improve lots of comments.
(url_to_non_existent_url_path): Adjust the expected error message as it is
slightly different with the shims in place.
